column5: I am here. Just wanna say i can support you. Like i think.

Hah, if you have bros, who love you and take care of you... Just fuckin' might take care of you, dat's great if you just have friends to talk with. But l haven't. There's nobody around me l can to talk with, so sometimes i am just talking to myself. Haha. Fuck. 

Oh, l'm like a shitty whiner.
